{"tid":1069511,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[港產片] MMA 格鬥戲《入鐵籠》討論","createTime":"2019-03-20T04:29:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-28T16:12:12.000Z","uid":15213,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"a892ba13e0a2832dd9a353a799ae4cb7ae74b881","tid":1069511,"uid":15213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T04:29:36.000Z","msg":"聽日上但唔多見有宣傳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇咗或者想睇就入嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i3OJLwZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi3OJLwZ.png&h=12a98298&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oh3mxb0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foh3mxb0.png&h=4cab8ed2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n導演: 陳翊恆<br />\n主演: 林耀聲, 馬志威, 楊柳青, 葛民輝, 元秋, 鄭麗莎<br />\n<br />\n簡介：<br />\n哥哥『招積』〈馬志威 飾〉和弟弟『電兔』〈林耀聲 飾〉在孤兒院長大，經院工『雷Sir』〈葛民輝 飾〉領養並得到『雷師母』〈元秋 飾〉的幫忙，入住鄉村拳館。招積供養弟弟讀書，但電兔因打地下拳賺錢，被開除學籍，兩兄弟因而反目。<br />\n...<br />\n及後，網絡卻瘋傳「爛仔交王」電兔為了哥哥挑戰『萬人迷』陳樂風的片段。兩兄弟回想起當年在孤兒院的日子，忍不住流下淚來。哥哥說電兔有一個特別的天賦，就是可迅速判斷對手拳法的能力，使他能輕易閃避攻擊。所謂「精確勝於能力、時機超越速度」，招積卻一直隱瞞著，是怕有一天弟弟會打贏自己...<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ywi05a62dn4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fywi05a62dn4&d=0gDP8yh%2BwNUcUrQXLcOs9KooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=a1b853cb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ywi05a62dn4</a>"},{"pid":"6b08ba0e1ba77d1e679ac88952291e9178adc65b","tid":1069511,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T09:33:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"355d64a0e6cd73803e3573f1117195280f653340","tid":1069511,"uid":194415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T09:35:23.000Z","msg":"支持！<br />\n<br />\nd graphic 真係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb25793bd12b28cabb97193b297717b79f0b438","tid":1069511,"uid":10398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T