 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dbefee5831501fe4e319364189d8cfa45ec6e02","tid":1069511,"uid":54019,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:39:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔錯，咁呢類片都離不開講失敗後再贏<br />\n演員都做得唔錯，林耀聲同馬志威同埋做陳樂風個三位演員都印象深刻，而且又唔離地，日頭打兩份兼職先維持到所謂的「夢想」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過真心少人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日睇個場加埋我得三個人<br />\n都希望有多d唔同類型港產片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5708c3e53e3c7959395d85a99fd7688d6252d7","tid":1069511,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dbefee5831501fe4e319364189d8cfa45ec6e02","tid":1069511,"uid":54019,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:39:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔錯，咁呢類片都離不開講失敗後再贏<br />\n演員都做得唔錯，林耀聲同馬志威同埋做陳樂風個三位演員都印象深刻，而且又唔離地，日頭打兩份兼職先維持到所謂的「夢想」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過真心少人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日睇個場加埋我得三個人<br />\n都希望有多d唔同類型港產片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T15:09:35.000Z","msg":"就係喺星影匯？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf7a9ed891acf090b57517193d28ab8fd1c49654","tid":1069511,"uid":3172,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T15:42:23.000Z","msg":"除左中間偷拍個段on9到爆炸   其他部分都ok<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw  女主好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31220ab5b02c4bca00709a6d7370680647947c2c","tid":1069511,"uid":54019,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9c5708c3e53e3c7959395d85a99fd7688d6252d7","tid":1069511,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9dbefee5831501fe4e319364189d8cfa45ec6e02","tid":1069511,"uid":54019,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T12:39:35.000Z","msg":"我覺得唔錯，咁呢類片都離不開講失敗後再贏<br />\n演員都做得唔錯，林耀聲同馬志威同埋做陳樂風個三位演員都印象深刻，而且又唔離地，日頭打兩份兼職先維持到所謂的「夢想」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過真心少人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />今日睇個場加埋我得三個人<br />\n都希望有多d唔同類型港產片睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T15:09:35.000Z","msg":"就係喺星影匯？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T16:32:12.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e027c0fcded08ce81acab07d2a235c5e3b86585c","tid":1069511,"uid":146535,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T05:54:16.000Z","msg":"覺得劇情好「行」<br />\n打嘅時候有肉緊嘅感覺<br />\n例牌整啲訓練環節，可能自己做開運動，唔覺訓練嗰度有幾熱血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似好賣貼地，日頭返工夜晚練野<br />\n但其實做開運動都係咁<br />\n後尾又幾好笑，話細佬有特別嘅格鬥資質<br />\n但其實阿哥又有幾重拳<br />\n輕人10 磅去打，最後又可以反擊返ko 對面<br />\n最大問題事前又冇講過乜野策略<br />\n剩係得第三局前阿哥講要打拳頭交<br />\n鬼唔知咩你摔技都冇練過（本來有諗過會唔會用巴柔）<br />\n平時都係打拳頭，突然變超西就贏左<br />\n至於對面又係戰敗強化，唔知套戲係咪想講有錢仔有人力物力資源都輸畀個「只要有心就贏到嘅傻仔」<br />\n<br />\n當我睇唔明你套戲<br />\n只係講自己感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e1567d06a0b66547e80ca9ec47f81790ac0be2","tid":1069511,"uid":30922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T14:16:50.000Z","msg":"幾好睇<br />\n不過大部份演員d戲好假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2525eaff585d70d64cbfc7eccf8254e87aae90bf","tid":1069511,"uid":155144,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T14:33:27.000Z","msg":"總括嚟講，係顏值擔當嘅電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n馬志威好撚型，估唔到文戲武戲都難唔倒佢<br />\n楊柳青明明好打得，但冇乜位比佢發揮到<br />\n林耀聲演技幾自然，但矮馬志威成個頭<br />\nwinkie可有可無"},{"pid":"d1e3d5131595e3829dd9ca06ddfd7da60803aae5","tid":1069511,"uid":28181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"355d64a0e6cd73803e3573f1117195280f653340","tid":1069511,"uid":194415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T09:35:23.000Z","msg":"支持！<br />\n<br />\nd graphic 真係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T16:37:36.000Z","msg":"拳賽poster<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5bc52f50fdc9d775333700fd3a7717d1e4d813b","tid":1069511,"uid":50216,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T17:02:35.000Z","msg":"楊柳青幾正下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aed331f4dac0190a01ddba528b79fa940effa9b7","tid":1069511,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:33:39.000Z","msg":"劇情無重心<br />\n無明顯起乘轉合<br />\nMMA無說服力"},{"pid":"e4fa491424c405617e185a7096b4558ff00efec7","tid":1069511,"uid":146535,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"aed331f4dac0190a01ddba528b79fa940effa9b7","tid":1069511,"uid":55913,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:33:39.000Z","msg":"劇情無重心<br />\n無明顯起乘轉合<br />\nMMA無說服力"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T04:39:34.000Z","msg":"以戲嚟講，我覺得劇情幾鬆散<br />\n內容方面，描寫MMA 唔算多<br />\n睇完成套戲唔知講左啲咩出嚟<br />\n過3 關嗰度都流流地<br />\n似儀式多過測試"}]}